text: Cathryn Rose "Casey" Wilson (born October 24, 1980) is an American comedian, actress and screenwriter. She played Penny Hartz in the ABC sitcom Happy Endings. For that, she was nominated twice for a Critics' Choice Television Award for Best Supporting Actress in a Comedy Series. Wilson's other major work includes Julie & Julia, Gone Girl and The Meddler. On Saturday Night Live, she had a two-season acting job from 2008 to 2009.
